{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangetheme"]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/OUDSTheme"],"kind":"relationships","type":"inheritsFrom","title":"Inherits From"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/SQ","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s16SendableMetatypeP"],"kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To"}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme\/init(borders:colors:colorModes:colorsCharts:colorsDecorative:effects:elevations:fonts:grids:opacities:dimensions:sizes:spaces:alert:badge:bar:bulletList:button:checkbox:chip:controlItem:divider:icon:link:pinCodeInput:quantityInput:radioButton:selectInput:skeleton:switch:tag:inputTag:textArea:textInput:resourcesBundle:name:fontFamily:tuning:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme is the bsic, default, theme for any Orange products."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is an override of the abtract "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"must be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It can override any properties from its superclass, and can be derived too."}],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B5ThemeC","roleHeading":"Class","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"symbolKind":"class","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeTheme"}],"title":"OrangeTheme","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeTheme","kind":"identifier"}]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeTheme"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Usages","level":1,"anchor":"Usages"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Any Orange products must use this theme. It provides core and Orange colors and any elements for sizings, spacings and dimensions for example."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The system font families are used; no "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helevetica","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family is embeded nor providd  by OUDS."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This theme also provides colors charts tokens."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The theme can be got through environment variable:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.theme) var theme"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Integration","level":2,"anchor":"Integration"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To use this theme, inject it to your view using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"type":"text","text":" and get it through environment variable."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    @main","    struct YourApp: App {","        var body: some Scene {","            WindowGroup {","                OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                    \/\/ Your root view","                }","            }","        }","    }"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Theme tuning","level":2,"anchor":"Theme-tuning"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The theme can be customized a bit for more flexibility thanks to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Tuning"},{"type":"text","text":" object."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You just need to give a predefined tuning configuration at theme init to build the one you need."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To apply the tuning:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your theme tuning","    let tuning = Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true, hasRoundedAlertMessages: true)","","    \/\/ Apply it to your theme","    let theme = OrangeTheme(tuning: tuning)","    \/\/ Or in one line","    let theme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning(hasRoundedButtons: true, hasRoundedTextInputs: true, hasRoundedAlertMessages: true))","","    \/\/ Or apply predefined tunings","    let orangeFranceTheme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeFrance)","    let orangeBusinessTheme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning.OrangeBusiness)","    let maxitTheme = OrangeTheme(tuning: Tuning.MaxIt)"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Typography","level":2,"anchor":"Typography"},{"type":"heading","text":"Helvetica Neue","level":3,"anchor":"Helvetica-Neue"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange brand strongly relies on the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family. Thus each Orange brand should, or must, use it."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For iOS the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family is available at system level, so it is not needed to get it through external assets."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"By default an instance of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" uses as font family the token "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault"},{"type":"text","text":", which is today "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use another font family, you will have to send the suitable token or the suitable font family."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, beware, iOS API relies also on the PostScript name of the font."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To be sure of the value to use, look at the font book of your device."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is recommended to use the font raw tokens."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ The following instanciations work","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme()","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(fontFamily: OrangeBrandFontRawTokens.familyBrandDefault)","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(fontFamily: \"HelveticaNeue\") \/\/ Which is PostScript name of the font","    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(fontFamily: \"Helvetica Neue\") \/\/ Which is font family nale"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic","level":3,"anchor":"Helvetica-Neue-Arabic"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Because the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" font family does not manage arabic alphabet but latin one, it is possible apply another font family to the theme like the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Helvetica Neue Arabic","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":". This font family assets can be retrieved through the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/brand.orange.com\/en\/brand-basics\/typography"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"PostScript name management has been implemented for this font family, thus the weight are managed and it is only needed to add the font assets to the project,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"register them and define the font family name to use."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    let orangeTheme = OrangeTheme(family: \"Helvetica Neue Arabic\")"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Tokens loading","level":2,"anchor":"Tokens-loading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can also use some tokens providers defined in your side, but they must match the same type as the one used on the themes (see "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":")."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["   \/\/ Use some already defined providers","   let borders = OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider()","   let sizes = OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider()","   let spaces = OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider()","","   \/\/ For example, use your own provider of color semantic tokens","   \/\/ It must inherit from OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider (which is instance of AllColorSemanticTokensProvider) or directly implement AllColorSemanticTokensProvider","   let colors = YourOwnColorSemanticTokensProvider()","","   \/\/ Some providers need other providers to use their tokens","   let button = OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider(sizes: sizes, borders: borders, colors: colors, spaces: spaces)","","   \/\/ But you can also use the providers as they are without assigning semantic tokens providers","   \/\/ and just use the default ones","   let badge = OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider()","","   \/\/ Define in the end your theme by overriding some providers.","   \/\/ You can override all providers, or only some, or just keep the theme as is.","   \/\/ However you should uses thhese providers in a dedicated Orange theme subclass for clarity reasons.","   let yourOwnOrangeTheme = OrangeTheme(colors: colors, borders: borders, sizes: sizes, spaces: spaces, button: button, badge: badge)"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Tokens versions","level":2,"anchor":"Tokens-versions"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Core OUDS version: 1.10.0"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Core Orange version: 1.2.0"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Brand Orange version: 2.5.0"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.8.0","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Since","style":"note"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeTheme"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandColorRawTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeBrandFontRawTokens"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Group","title":"Group"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","abstract":[{"text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","role":"collection","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"title":"Theme Orange"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeTheme/init(borders:colors:colorModes:colorsCharts:colorsDecorative:effects:elevations:fonts:grids:opacities:dimensions:sizes:spaces:alert:badge:bar:bulletList:button:checkbox:chip:controlItem:divider:icon:link:pinCodeInput:quantityInput:radioButton:selectInput:skeleton:switch:tag:inputTag:textArea:textInput:resourcesBundle:name:fontFamily:tuning:)":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Constructor of the Orange theme."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text